msgstr "अनुवादकानां_भूमिका"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a type of documentation. The documents are in a file format called "
"texinfo, and can be read on the command line with the <ulink url=\"info:/info"
"\"><command>info</command></ulink> program."
msgstr ""
"Info इति एकः प्रकारः दस्तावेजीकरणम् । दस्तावेजाः texinfo इति सञ्चिकास्वरूपेण सन्ति, "
"<ulink url=\"info:/info\"><command>info</command></ulink> कार्यक्रमेन सह "
"आदेशपङ्क्तौ पठितुं शक्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Info KIO worker allows you to read the info pages installed on your "
"system, from within &konqueror;. You can use it very easily:"
msgstr ""
"Info KIO कार्यकर्ता भवन्तं भवतः प्रणाल्यां संस्थापितानि info पृष्ठानि पठितुं शक्नोति, "
"&konqueror;. भवान् अतीव सुलभतया तस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति:"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<userinput><command>info:</command><replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"userinput> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This would show you the top level node of the Info documentation for the "
"&gcc; compiler."
msgstr "एतेन भवन्तः &gcc; संकलकः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info is a &GNU; replacement for <command>man</command>, but is not widely "
"used outside of &GNU; software."
msgstr ""
"Info इति &GNU; <command>man</command> इत्यस्य प्रतिस्थापनम्, परन्तु &GNU; तन्त्रांश।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can quite easily browse the info documentation you have installed from "
"within the &khelpcenter; application, or you can use the info KIO worker "
"directly from within both &konqueror; and the mini-cli."
msgstr ""
"भवान् &khelpcenter; अनुप्रयोगं, अथवा भवान् info KIO कार्यकर्तारं प्रत्यक्षतया द्वयोः "
"अन्तः &konqueror; लघु-क्लि इति च ।"
